comment: West (IND) sets the screen on Williams (BKN) and he gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Hill (IND) and Johnson (BKN) briefly engage on the perimeter while Johnson is moving to get the ball.
Hill (IND) does not affect Johnson's (BKN) RSBQ at the start of his drive.
Hibbert (IND) cleanly blocks Johnson's (BKN) driving floater.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Young (BKN) was upheld and Indiana was awarded possession.
Young (BKN) and West (IND) briefly engage while battling for rebounding position.
Hill (IND) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Johnson (BKN) on the perimeter.
As Jack (BKN) trails Watson (IND) on the baseline, West (IND) sets a screen while out of bounds.
Watson (IND) commits a take foul on Jack (BKN).
Rudez (IND) requests and is granted a timeout in less than 5 seconds during the inbounds.
Rudez (IND) commits a take foul on Jack (BKN).
